  "id": "RAW_717950f1",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-12-5）：南洋理工与商汤科技开源 NEO，重构视觉语言模型技术范式，达成 VLM 性能与效率平衡",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500742&idx=1&sn=7c4c3651874f355f69fe59c269fc4731",
  "date": "2025-12-05 10:24:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：NEO</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"484\" data-imgfileid=\"100017080\" data-ratio=\"0.41759259259259257\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1158\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8c0015a4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDky8pkw0oickM9MNopLXD4KTO7ibYaAIZSE7rfzftmwZgvvbLD4Rf20OkmyhFVkk1MvXeGI4xawRvyWg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★NEO项目旨在开发原生的视觉语言模型（VLM），通过统一像素-词编码、对齐和推理，提供一种密集的单体模型架构。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">NEO在仅使用3.9亿图文示例的情况下，从零开始发展出强大的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">视觉感知能力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，性能媲美</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">顶级模块化VLM</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，并超越其他原生VLM。项目还提供了多种可重用组件，促进了一个具有成本效益和可扩展的生态系统。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/neo\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/neo</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：hito</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"350\" data-imgfileid=\"100017078\" data-ratio=\"0.30092592592592593\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c53710a6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDky8pkw0oickM9MNopLXD4KTOps3KhIh77wUnulJapIXSPu9jDjO9mcPSu30bcUtVO7SV8ZWU6ItAow%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Hito 1.7B是一个实验性模型，旨在通过知识蒸馏技术将大型模型的认知架构转移到较小的模型中。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型经过Hito-Genius生成的约300个高质量推理示例的微调，展示了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">小型模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">在有限数据下学习结构化思维的能力。虽然不是生产级别的模型，但它证明了认知架构的可转移性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hito\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hito</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：VR-Bench</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"546\" data-imgfileid=\"100017081\" data-ratio=\"0.46944444444444444\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1aeedbab&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDky8pkw0oickM9MNopLXD4KTOQpdCc99Q1wia9cfr8GR9M1DmD09wZGriaYHmz2yddb852WO0SnnwzRJA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★VR-Bench是一个综合性基准，用于通过各种益智游戏评估视觉语言模型（VLMs）在空间推理和规划任务上的表现。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它提供了一个统一的框架用于数据集生成、评估和分析。VR-Bench采用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">视频推理的新范式</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，通过迷宫解题视频生成来探测多模态推理能力，显示出微调后的视频模型在长时间空间规划任务上持续优于强大的VLMs。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/vrbench\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/vrbench</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：TRIM-KV</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"446\" data-imgfileid=\"100017079\" data-ratio=\"0.38425925925925924\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1160\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=500b7c1d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDky8pkw0oickM9MNopLXD4KTO0raVdcsr7rcrbq2ONoVMa6sQN2SFjxPm896ia5d6Pa0tkESK1kmrdBg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★TRIM-KV 是一种高效且可学习的键值驱逐策略，旨在提高大语言模型（LLMs）在长时间推理中的效率。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过在创建时学习每个键值对的内在重要性，并随着时间的推移指数衰减这种重要性，TRIM-KV 模拟了标准推理中的驱逐过程。与依赖查询的注意力分数不同，TRIM-KV 的保留分数是查询无关的，捕捉了令牌的长期效用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/trim-kv\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/trim-kv</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：smallevals</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"504\" data-imgfileid=\"100017077\" data-ratio=\"0.43333333333333335\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=169fafe1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDky8pkw0oickM9MNopLXD4KTOxLE3icKwXNkBw5VVdBeezb4ISN0HTFxBQoz7lLHtWwBQ2keMmMa4dXw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★smallevals是一个轻量级的评估框架，专为RAG（Retrieval-Augmented Generation）系统设计，使用小型的0.6B模型进行快速的离线检索评估。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该框架可以在CPU、GPU或MPS上本地运行，并支持连接任意向量数据库。它能够在几秒内完成GPU上的评估，或在几分钟内完成CPU上的评估，提供了一种高效且免费的解决方案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/smallevals\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/smallevals</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：LatentMAS</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"566\" data-imgfileid=\"100017082\" data-ratio=\"0.4888888888888889\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1158\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=322e2681&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDky8pkw0oickM9MNopLXD4KTOETKlwujlMGs4DmuUWQYfeaoG1trQEC5JJBw86Fb6XRxmm5FiaQPZBicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★LatentMAS是一个多智能体推理框架，将智能体协作从文本空间转移到模型的潜在空间。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过在各自的工作记忆中传递潜在思维，智能体无需生成冗长的文本推理轨迹。LatentMAS具有</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">高效的多步推理、训练无关的潜在空间</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">对齐等特点，兼容任何HuggingFace模型，并可选用vLLM后端。总体而言，LatentMAS在多智能体系统中实现了更优的性能、更低的token使用量和显著的时间加速。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/latent-mas\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/latent-mas</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章聚合发布了南洋理工与商汤科技合作的视觉语言模型 NEO 等多项最新开源 AI 项目，涵盖 VLM、LLM 效率、RAG 评估及多智能体系统，旨在平衡性能与效率。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章聚合发布了南洋理工与商汤科技合作的视觉语言模型 NEO 等多项最新开源 AI 项目，涵盖 VLM、LLM 效率、RAG 评估及多智能体系统，旨在平衡性能与效率。",
  "summary": "本文作为一篇“今日开源”汇总，介绍了六个最新的 AI 开源项目。其中，南洋理工与商汤科技联合开源的 NEO 项目，致力于构建原生的视觉语言模型（VLM），通过统一像素-词编码实现性能与效率的平衡，并在有限数据下达到顶级 VLM 的水平。此外，还包括了 Hito，一个利用知识蒸馏技术将大型模型认知架构转移到小型模型的实验性项目；VR-Bench，一个评估 VLM 空间推理和规划能力的综合性基准；TRIM-KV，一种提高大语言模型（LLMs）长时间推理效率的键值驱逐策略；smallevals，一个轻量级的 RAG 系统离线检索评估框架；以及 LatentMAS，一个通过潜在空间实现智能体高效协作的多智能体推理框架。文章对每个项目进行了简要介绍，并提供了 SOTA 模型平台的收藏链接。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "NEO 项目重构 VLM 技术范式，通过原生架构实现性能与效率的平衡。",
      "explanation": "NEO 作为原生视觉语言模型，通过统一编码从零开始发展视觉感知能力，在有限数据下性能媲美顶级模块化 VLM，并提供成本效益和可扩展的生态系统。"
    },
    {
